dct_description_sm: Relief is shown by rock drawing. "Surveyed by Svy. Div. C.L. & S.O. P.W.D. Hong Kong 1958." Map shows future and proposed reclamation lines. Includes Hong Kong - Kwoolon index of relevant buildings. Map is part of a set. Map Collection has sheet 196 only [it is a photocopy]. "Crown copyright reserved".
dct_creator_sm: Hong Kong. Public Works Department. Survey Division
dct_publisher_sm: Hong Kong : Public Works Department. Survey Division, 1958.
